{"tid":2296999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金馬得獎短片《夜更》 今晚9:30果燃台獨家首播！","createTime":"2020-11-23T02:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:35:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa9489a217ade9b86ef978b791d913aa1ef5530","tid":2296999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/T6WEZZ2Y4JAE7FP4LF7S7HKMQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FT6WEZZ2Y4JAE7FP4LF7S7HKMQA%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT6gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=2f3c58f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201123%2FT6WEZZ2Y4JAE7FP4LF7S7HKMQA%2F&h=e3c67a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201123/T6WEZZ2Y4JAE7FP4LF7S7HKMQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》訂戶尊享丨金馬得獎短片《夜更》 今晚9:30果燃台獨家首播！<br />\n果燃電影丨《夜更》獨家首播<br />\n<br />\n香港人應該很久沒有這樣高興過。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台灣金馬丨反送中《夜更》奪最佳劇情短片 逆權《迷航》獲最佳紀錄片<br />\n<br />\n由《十年．浮瓜》導演郭臻執導、故事圍繞反送中抗爭的《夜更》，剛剛捧走台灣金馬最佳劇情短片獎。電影將在今晚9時30分在果燃台《蘋果》果燃台獨家首播，供《蘋果》訂戶尊享收看，與同路人一起分享這份遲來的喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PPlahu0sGecawIwD0pxVq4U9LOo=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YWQEOWANUVC43MK3ERGS4YE5KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPPlahu0sGecawIwD0pxVq4U9LOo%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYWQEOWANUVC43MK3ERGS4YE5KM.jpg&h=a82d822c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n今年7月之後，相信沒有人會再懷疑郭導的非凡洞察力。《浮瓜》裏的寓言變預言，不幸言中國安法的山雨欲來，只是還未到十年。同樣是小人物小故事，但《夜更》採用較為寫實手法，以藍絲的士司機 （蔡志強飾）的視角，在反送中示威期間，接載不同政見的乘客作為故事切入點，而他所遇到的人和事，都觸動了他的心理變化。電影滲入了去年反送中示威的真實畫面，令它更富現場感及真實感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vssIyIsndf4ExJa--4YjvCFy22Y=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6FTNAR6IOVDQJAMK2FM6HFLB5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvssIyIsndf4ExJa--4YjvCFy22Y%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6FTNAR6IOVDQJAMK2FM6HFLB5Y.jpg&h=fafe651e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dKXR7JjxRoiwzzQ7dA2fggOgFK0=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7PP2KL7C5BGF3A52CSAWR5GNS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdKXR7JjxRoiwzzQ7dA2fggOgFK0%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7PP2KL7C5BGF3A52CSAWR5GNS4.jpg&h=d76ce8f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n郭導用這種比較抽離手法去記載這紛亂時代，是絕頂聰明。《夜更》沒有既定立場，因它要表述的並不是黃藍鬥爭，也沒有說教式地批判那邊陣營的不是。相反郭導想透過影像去說故事，讓看倌自行判斷誰對誰錯。當然，郭導的幽默本色滲滿短片之中，就如當藍絲乘客說到「曱甴仔唔抵可憐，男姦女殺就啱」時，司機突然爆出「Ｘ你咩，盲嘅咩你！」而那對話是在回應藍絲乘客，還是在咒罵胡亂切線的馬路炸彈。郭導的箇中意圖，大概也不需太「畫公仔畫出腸」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l6cwWSOSgLfzZbu4pHVW_i002_o=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EHHDNERLERDMBBVNHMUZKC52JU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl6cwWSOSgLfzZbu4pHVW_i002_o%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEHHDNERLERDMBBVNHMUZKC52JU.jpg&h=d492f522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n演員方面，「一哥」蔡志強飾演的淺藍司機演得非常精采。本身為東區區議員的他，平日總是官仔骨骨，但片中的他卻大相徑庭，無論是其市井造型，抑或其粗口運用的精準到位，令觀眾能會心發笑之餘，甚至能代入藍絲的處境，慢慢同情他們生意受損的遭遇。隨着故事發展，透過司機的內心轉變與良知喚醒，自當然對他更有好感。「黃藍是政見，黑白是良知」，我們在《夜更》裏感受更深。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8vXqdFyHuX_w4G1vC1LUcx_Ib2E=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGSU6DRFARH53DGOXSFDX32G3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8vXqdFyHuX_w4G1vC1LUcx_Ib2E%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGSU6DRFARH53DGOXSFDX32G3A.jpg&h=1e9bb42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vBkS5DltXah5ABz-cFpWeC4L4kI=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHIUVBETHRH57EUKNGZHA2SPV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvBkS5DltXah5ABz-cFpWeC4L4kI%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHIUVBETHRH57EUKNGZHA2SPV4.jpg&h=4de4a907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照<br />\n<br />\n郭導透過代領人致謝時，明言《夜更》屬於「世界每個不同角落而又擁抱良知的香港人」。我們活在大時代的漩渦裏，注定難以獨善其身，每項決定的選擇，由我們的良知去決定。究竟要「擇善固執」？還是「隨波逐流」？相信看完《夜更》會有更透澈的想法。<br />\n<br />\n出爐金馬最佳劇情短片《夜更》，今晚9點30分在《蘋果》果燃台獨家首播。《蘋果》訂戶獨家尊享，萬勿錯過！<br />\n<br />\n果燃台 | 果迷專屬嘅影片世界<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n果燃台 link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT6gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=db5593c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel&h=12ef0e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel</a>"},{"pid":"3f664bf8e762679bfc192a44d4d8049c8c6c6b58","tid":2296999,"uid":